13:55.035 --> 13:58.837
<i>Then the gun arrived,
and she tried old faithful.</i>

13:58.839 --> 14:01.206
I hope that gun is
more important to you than sex.

14:01.208 --> 14:03.975
What?

14:07.180 --> 14:08.479
