14:08.481 --> 14:10.248
You know, once she...
She calms down,

14:10.250 --> 14:12.116
she'll come crawling back
to get this loving.

14:12.118 --> 14:13.151
No, she won't.

14:13.153 --> 14:15.453
I know.

14:15.455 --> 14:17.222
I know.

14:17.224 --> 14:19.357
