14:55.295 --> 14:57.495
Don't worry, guys.
I know karate.

14:57.497 --> 14:58.663
What's on your head?
Yeah.

14:58.665 --> 15:00.265
Oh.

15:00.267 --> 15:01.599
Mop the floor!
Mop the floor!

15:01.601 --> 15:03.101
Okay, okay.

15:03.103 --> 15:04.969
Okay, everybody calm down,
all right?

15:04.971 --> 15:06.938
I'm just gonna check
the security cameras.

15:06.940 --> 15:09.207
Oh, I took the Liberty of
