15:29.496 --> 15:30.962
Okay, okay.

15:30.964 --> 15:32.263
Oh, my goodness.
Dre!

15:32.265 --> 15:34.432
Why do they put so much tape
on these things?

15:34.434 --> 15:36.067
[ Grunts ]
Okay.

15:36.069 --> 15:37.602
Got it. Where is it?
Where is it?

