I-i-i was just...

16:09.169 --> 16:12.236
Flapping. In.
The breeze.

16:12.238 --> 16:13.304
Go!

16:13.306 --> 16:16.207
Go to your rooms.

16:16.209 --> 16:18.576
Way to turn it on dad to
distract from your cyber fail.

16:23.016 --> 16:24.482
I'm so disappointed in myself.

16:24.484 --> 16:26.150
In yourself?
But...

16:26.152 --> 16:27.685
So does that mean
I'm off the hook?

16:27.687 --> 16:31.322
Dre, I hate guns more than
I hate how Levi's fit me.

16:31.324 --> 16:33.157
And I know I don't want guns
anywhere near my children,

16:33.159 --> 16:34.158
all right?

16:34.160 --> 16:36.294
But somehow I panicked, okay?

16:36.296 --> 16:38.463
And that is how
people wind up shot.

16:38.465 --> 16:41.132
That is exactly why we shouldn't
have a gun in the house.

16:41.134 --> 16:42.400
Babe, I get it.

16:42.402 --> 16:44.102
And I shouldn't
want one, either,

16:44.104 --> 16:45.236
especially after
what just happened.

16:45.238 --> 16:46.671
But I do.

16:46.672 --> 16:48.105
Okay, you have to
explain this to me.

16:48.108 --> 16:49.574
