shoulder to see what was coming.

17:05.258 --> 17:08.493
A drive-by,
people getting jumped, jacked.

17:08.495 --> 17:10.294
There was always something.

17:10.296 --> 17:13.031
And when that's your childhood,
it feels like

17:13.033 --> 17:14.532
the only way to keep yourself
from being a victim

17:14.534 --> 17:17.101
is to have a gun.

17:17.103 --> 17:19.337
And as much as I want to
get that out of my mind, bow,

17:19.339 --> 17:20.538
I can't.

17:20.540 --> 17:22.073
Dre, why didn't you ever
tell me that?

17:22.075 --> 17:22.807
[ Sighs ]

17:22.809 --> 17:25.243
Babe, I don't know.

17:25.245 --> 17:28.479
